## Overall progress

From the uploaded structure, I'd estimate:

| Layer          | Completion |
| -------------- | ---------: |
| Domain         |        95% |
| Infrastructure |        90% |
| Application    |        15% |
| API            |        10% |
| Testing        |         0% |
| Documentation  |         5% |

Overall, you're around **50% complete**. The remaining work is concentrated in the Application and API layers. Once you implement the CQRS handlers, validators, DTOs, and controllers, the project will move from an architectural skeleton to a functional application.
